data.description: Showings Begin with the Open House April 28th from 12-3PM. Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom twin home in Lehighton that offers a perfect blend of original  details and modern amenities. The first floor features beautiful woodwork details, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious kitchen includes a convenient first floor laundry and pantry area, perfect for storage and organization. One of the highlights of this home is the finished, heated attic space, which could serve as a 4th bedroom or a versatile rec/gaming room. Imagine the possibilities for this bonus space! Step outside to the rear deck and enjoy a panoramic Mountain View, providing a peaceful retreat right in your own backyard. Let's not forget the natural gas furnace that was installed in 2022 and provides an economical way to keep your home warm.  The location of this home is ideal, with easy access to the D&L Trail, historic Jim Thorpe, shopping, restaurants, and major highways, including the entrance to the NE extension of the PA Turnpike. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely twin home your own in the heart of Lehighton.
